{
  "doc_id": "57331",
  "text": "For bacterial drug property analysis, drug targets were taken from TTD and PDTD databases. The datasets consisted of 285 bacterial targets from TTD and 187 bacterial targets from PDTD. A total of 472 targets were taken for prediction and analyses of the properties. These data were collected by using the combination of search terms viz. bacteria drug target, bacterial drug target and bacteria in both the databases. Thereafter, redundant results were removed and rest of the drug targets were used for the analyses. TTD can be accessed at http://bidd.nus.edu.sg/group/cjttd/ [CITATION_1] and PDTD can be accessed at www.dddc.ac.cn/pdtd/ [CITATION_2] .",
